overview:
FoundersList is your definitive source for quality resources, connections and communities within the Entrepreneurial landscape in San Diego and beyond.

A community of founders that share and exchange information about resources for founders in San Diego and around the globe. Need a lawyer for incorporation? Need a webdesigner for your proof of concept? need help with your financial statements or projections? If you need a pro - Check out the directory and see what others have to say, who they have used, and what they have experienced. We encourage you to leave comments for others to read.
